        <!-- TYPEAHEAD -->
        <section id="accordionsMarkup">
            <header class="content-block bg-light-grey">
                <div class="container">
                    <h3>Typeahead structure</h3>
                    <p>The Typeahead element uses the feature rich <a
                            href="https://github.com/jshjohnson/Choices" target="_blank"><code>choices.js</code></a>
                        library to wrap an ordinary select dropdown.</p>
                    <p>A Typeahead element is created using an existing select and the Typeahead js
                        module <code>data-js-module="typeAhead"</code>.</p>
                    <p>A Typeahead element options are defined by the <code>data-options</code> attribute, which
                        accepts a JSON string of options, where <code>value</code> is the value of the option, <code>label</code> is what is displayed and
                        <code>customProperties.description</code> is what is searchable.</p>
                    <p>A Typeahead element default option is defined by the <code>data-default</code> attribute,
                        which accepts the value of one of your JSON options.</p>
                    <p>You can also specify the css classes to style the container, select and dropdown via the <code>data-container-class</code>, <code>data-select-class</code>
                        and <code>data-dropdown-class</code> attributes.</p>
                    <p>By default the classes <code>.typeahead .form__field</code>, <code>.form__control</code> and <code>.typeahead__list .typeahead__list--dropdown .form__control</code>, respectively, will be applied.</p>

{{> snippet-typeahead }}

                </div>
            </header>

            <!-- DEFAULT SELECT -->
            <section id="defaultSelect">
                <div class="content-block">
                    <div class="container">
                        <h3>Default Select</h3>

                        <div class="form__group">
                            <label class="form__label">Select</label>

                            <select data-js-module="typeAhead"
                                    data-options='[{"value":"1","label":"One","customProperties":{"description":"One"}},{"value":"2","label":"Two","customProperties":{"description":"Two"}}]'
